35 class LengthCalculator
36 {
37 public:
38  LengthCalculator(LengthCalculator *parent)
39  : parent_(parent)
40  {
41  }
42 
43  virtual Void setLength()
44  {
45  if (parent_)
46  parent_->calculateLength();
47  }
48 
49  virtual uint16_t length() const = 0;
50  virtual uint16_t packedLength() const = 0;
51 
52 protected:
53  virtual uint16_t calculateLength() = 0;
54 
55 private:
56  LengthCalculator *parent_;
57 };
58 
59 class IEHeader : public LengthCalculator
60 {
61 public:
62  uint16_t type() const { return hdr_.type; }
63  IEHeader &type(uint16_t type) { hdr_.type = type; return *this; }
64 
65  uint16_t length() const { return hdr_.len; }
66  uint16_t packedLength() const { return hdr_.len > 0 ? hdr_.len + sizeof(hdr_) : 0; }
67  Void setLength() { hdr_.len = calculateLength(); LengthCalculator::setLength(); }
68  Bool present() const { return hdr_.len != 0; }
69 
70  pfcp_ie_header_t &header() { return hdr_; }
71 
72 protected:
73  IEHeader(pfcp_ie_header_t &hdr, uint16_t type, LengthCalculator *parent)
74  : LengthCalculator(parent),
75  hdr_(hdr)
76  {
77  IEHeader::type(type);
78  }
79 
80  virtual uint16_t calculateLength() = 0;
81 
82 private:
83  IEHeader();
84  pfcp_ie_header_t &hdr_;
85 };
